"{\"uid\": \"rollingstone.com-music-music-news-celine-dion-olympics-performance-paris-full-of-joy-1235069317\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByTom\\u00e1s Mier  C\\u00e9line Dion is feeling \\\"so happy\\\" after hergrand Eiffel Tower performanceat the opening ceremony of the 2024 ParisOlympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 25, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"C\\u00e9line Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Canadian star shared a sweet message on social media celebrating the moment as she congratulated the athletes participating in the games.\", \"from\": 138, \"to\": 279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 142, \"end\": 150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9967056250671286, \"rank\": 0.0018937316366873097, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am honored to have performed tonight, for the Paris 2024 Opening Ceremony, and so full of joy to be back in one of my very favorite cities!\\\"\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion wrote.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most of all, I am so happy to be celebrating these amazing athletes, with all their stories of sacrifice and determination, pain and perseverance.\\\"\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am honored to have performed tonight, for the Paris 2024 Opening Ceremony, and so full of joy to be back in one of my very favorite cities!\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of all, I am so happy to be celebrating these amazing athletes, with 